  "prompt": "How do I report a bug/loophole on Quora? What will I get for that?",
  "response": "To report a bug or issue on Quora:\n\n1. Go to the Quora Help Center\n2. Click on \"Contact Us\" or \"Report a Problem\"\n3. Select the specific type of issue you're experiencing\n4. Provide detailed information about the bug/loophole\n5. Submit the report\n\nTypically, you won't receive direct compensation for reporting a bug. However, Quora may:\n- Thank you for your report\n- Investigate the issue\n- Potentially fix the bug\n- In some cases, provide credits or minor recognition\n\nSignificant or security-related bug reports might receive more attention, but there's no guaranteed reward system.\n\nIf you discover a serious security vulnerability, it's best to report it through their official channels responsibly.",
